Text:
Would help much better if there was a list besides the pack.
Downloading 3,5 GiB without knowing what it is, is quite tough.

Sorry, it's quite difficult to give a list what is inside of each pack. I'm going to organize this collection later.

Basically the collection is organized in folders, but...you'll see!

The whole package contains about 55000 files. There are eBooks (pdf, chm, doc), exe, pics, html, source codes etc.

Yeah, making a more organized index would be awesome, still, thanks for it anyway, but making a short index would help, even just listing the different book titles or dates. Impressive amounts of info, good job.
very much agreed very impressive, as the others mentioned even a small index would be ideal, good work =)

I can't download 3.42 GiB without knowing more about these books, but I'm interested enough to download Books1.rar, and when I check it all out, I will post the contents of it.  Anyone else who is checking this torrent out, download other pieces and list the contents.  Team work, guys, team work ;]
